## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-102">次の表は、現在サポートされているオプションを示しています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-103">カテゴリ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-104">設定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-105">値/効果</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-106">コントラクト (contract)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-107">継承</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-108">コントラクトの継承を有効にする `true`オフにするには `false` します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-109">既定では、 `true`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-110">runtime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-111">チェック</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9ec07-112">実行時チェックをオンにする `true`オフにするには `false` します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-113">既定では、 `true`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-114">次の例に示すように、この属性を使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-115">アセンブリ全体の実行時チェックをオフにするには、次のようにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-116">特定の型に対してランタイムコントラクトチェックをオンにするには、次のようにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9ec07-117">特定のメソッドに対してランタイムチェックをオフにするには、次の手順を実行します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ec07-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
